Vorgehensweise:

Komplettes SD image flashen von beagleboard.org (kernel 4.1.1, console)



Opkg static from github must be built (using a newer toolchain url?
	arm-2014.05-29-arm-none-linux-gnueabi-i686-pc-linux-gnu.tar.bz2 (from https://github.com/maximeh/buildroot/blob/master/toolchain/toolchain-external/toolchain-external.mk)


opkg has hardcoded strings to overlayfs, those need to be symliked: script: symlink_opkg_dirs.sh

Installieren der radarcape software:

apt-get update; apt-get -y install libsqlite0 connman psmisc

*** opkg muss gepatcht werden ***
RADARCAPE_DIR=/home/root in preinst und postinst script muss auf /root geändert werden

***
opkg-static install .... --force-depends 


Watchdog disable für development:

echo 60 > /sys/class/gpio/export
echo out > /sys/class/gpio/gpio60/direction
echo 1 > /sys/class/gpio/gpio60/value
echo 0 > /sys/class/gpio/gpio60/value
(while `true`; do echo 1 > /sys/class/gpio/gpio60/value; echo 0 > /sys/class/gpio/gpio60/value; sleep 30; done)&


beaglebone dts-overlay installieren: (die restlichen files die in /lib/firmware gehören. u.a. BB-UART5 und BB-UART2)
cd /tmp
git clone https://github.com/beagleboard/bb.org-overlays.git
cd bb.org-overlays
./dtc-overlay.sh
./install.sh
cd ..
rm -rf bb.org-overlays

dtc -O dtb -o BB-B-Radarcape-00A0.dtbo -b 0 -@ BB-B-Radarcape.dts # recompile dts file for the new dtc version!
reboot
